  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion, carrot, and celery and cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the Thai green curry paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chicken to the pan and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add the coconut milk, water, salt, and black pepper to the pan and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in the chopped cilantro and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Serve the curry hot over rice or with naan bread."
